text: The girls' doubles tournament of the 2019 Badminton Asia Junior Championships will be held from 24 to 28 July. Febriana Dwipuji Kusuma / Ribka Sugiarto from Indonesia clinched this title in the last edition. ==Seeds== Seeds were announced on 2 July.Individual events seeds # Nita Violina Marwah / Putri Syaikah (Second round) # Li Yijing / Luo Xumin (Champions) # Febriana Dwipuji Kusuma / Amalia Cahaya Pratiwi (Second round) # Lin Fangling / Zhou Xinru (Semifinals) ==Draw== ===Finals=== ===Top Half=== ====Section 1==== ====Section 2==== ===Bottom half=== ====Section 3==== ====Section 4==== == References == == External links == *Main Draw Category:2019 Badminton Asia Junior Championships
